    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-01-05T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-01-05T00:00:00-05:00" n="390" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d390">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Foster</persName> to Mr.
                                <persName type="to">Snowden</persName>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department
                                    of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-01-05">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 5,
                            1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Caroline claim must not be complicated with other questions. The President
                        expects complete settlement without delay. Advise progress by telegraph. New
                        Spanish minister should bring full instructions as to Mora and other old
                        claims.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Foster.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
